---
title: 图 2-1 Agent 架构图
---

graph TB
    UserInstruction["📝 用户任务指令
    示例: '登录 example.com 并提取订阅链接'"]

    subgraph Coordinator["🎯 CoordinatorAgent
    （协调代理 - 总指挥）"]
        CoordDuty["职责:
        • 解析用户指令，识别需要执行的操作序列
        • 按依赖顺序调用子代理工具
        • 汇总各子代理的执行结果
        • 生成统一的结构化输出"]
        CoordOutput["输出: CoordinatorOutput
        {status, message, error_type,
        operations_executed, operations_results}"]
    end

    subgraph SubAgents["🤖 子代理群"]
        LoginAgent["LoginAgent
        （登录）

        职责: 网站登录、凭证填充、状态确认
        输出: LoginOutput"]

        RegisterAgent["RegisterAgent
        （注册）

        职责: 账号注册、邮箱验证、信息保存
        输出: RegisterOutput"]

        ExtractAgent["ExtractAgent
        （数据提取）

        职责: 订阅提取、链接解析、结果返回
        输出: ExtractOutput"]

        EvidenceAgent["EvidenceAgent
        （取证）

        职责: 菜单遍历、截图取证、报告生成
        输出: EvidenceOutput"]

        PaymentAgent["PaymentAgent
        （支付）

        职责: 支付导航、二维码定位、截图保存
        输出: PaymentOutput"]
    end

    subgraph ExternalTools["🔧 外部工具"]
        Playwright["🌐 Playwright
        MCP Server

        提供浏览器
        自动化能力"]
        Email["📧 Email
        IMAP

        验证码获取
        邮件解析"]
    end

    UserInstruction --> Coordinator

    Coordinator -.->|as_tool()| LoginAgent
    Coordinator -.->|as_tool()| RegisterAgent
    Coordinator -.->|as_tool()| ExtractAgent
    Coordinator -.->|as_tool()| EvidenceAgent
    Coordinator -.->|as_tool()| PaymentAgent

    LoginAgent --> Playwright
    RegisterAgent --> Playwright
    RegisterAgent --> Email
    ExtractAgent --> Playwright
    EvidenceAgent --> Playwright
    PaymentAgent --> Playwright

    style UserInstruction fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1976d2,stroke-width:2px
    style Coordinator fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#7b1fa2,stroke-width:3px
    style Playwright fill:#ffebee,stroke:#c62828,stroke-width:2px
    style Email fill:#ffebee,stroke:#c62828,stroke-width:2px
    style LoginAgent fill:#e1f5fe,stroke:#0277bd,stroke-width:2px
    style RegisterAgent fill:#e1f5fe,stroke:#0277bd,stroke-width:2px
    style ExtractAgent fill:#e1f5fe,stroke:#0277bd,stroke-width:2px
    style EvidenceAgent fill:#e1f5fe,stroke:#0277bd,stroke-width:2px
    style PaymentAgent fill:#e1f5fe,stroke:#0277bd,stroke-width:2px
